<h2>Finials as Lightning Rods</h2>
Most finials, with at least a minimum thickness of 3/16â€³, can be a lightning rod. Â Solar InnovationsÂ®Â recommends a full lightning protection system for all structures. Therefore, customers should bond the metal structure to its own earth-ground or tie it directly to an existing buildingâ€™s grounding system.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]
